Project_Title: miRNA profiling of Hek293T & Chick Notochord cells derived Exosomes
Project_Description: In this study, we show that Shh is secreted on two types of exo-vesicles by human cell lines . We find that the two classes of exo-vesicles carry distinct signal-modulatory accessory proteins as well as distinct sets of cellular miRNAs.
